English: Choose the number of consistent taps required for calculating the respiratory rate.

Amharic: የአተነፋፈስ መጠን ላማስላት የሚያገለግለውን ተመሳሰይ ንክኪ ብዛት ምረጪ

Not enough taps. Please try again.
